'''柯林·馬嘉露'''（{{lang-en|Colleen McCullough}}，{{bd|1937年|6月1日|2015年|1月29日}}），[[澳大利亚|澳大利亚]]作家。

出生於澳洲南威爾斯州，曾任美國[[康乃狄克州|康乃狄克州]]紐哈芬耶魯大學精神生理學教授。1977年著有《[[刺鳥|刺鳥]]》（The Thorn Birds）一書，成為澳洲最暢銷書。1997年被宣佈為澳洲「活著的國寶」，后定居英國劍橋。馬嘉露嗜抽煙，患有眼黃斑病變症，2003年9月左眼幾乎失明，右眼視力也急速退化中<ref>{{cite news |title=Colleen McCullough obituary |url=https://www.theguardian.com/books/2015/jan/30/colleen-mccullough |accessdate=2021-09-03 |work=the Guardian |date=2015-01-30 |language=en |archive-date=2021-09-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210903023520/https://www.theguardian.com/books/2015/jan/30/colleen-mccullough |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=McCullough unhampered by sight problems |url=https://www.smh.com.au/national/mccullough-unhampered-by-sight-problems-20051018-gdm9o2.html |accessdate=2021-09-03 |work=The Sydney Morning Herald |date=2005-10-17 |language=en |archive-date=2021-09-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210903023521/https://www.smh.com.au/national/mccullough-unhampered-by-sight-problems-20051018-gdm9o2.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2015年1月29日逝世<ref name="Los Angeles Times 2015">{{cite web | title=Colleen McCullough dies at 77; author of 'Thorn Birds,' mysteries | website=Los Angeles Times | date=2015-01-30 | url=https://www.latimes.com/local/obituaries/la-me-colleen-mccullough-dies-at-77-20150129-story.html | access-date=2021-09-03 | archive-date=2021-12-23 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211223201431/https://www.latimes.com/local/obituaries/la-me-colleen-mccullough-dies-at-77-20150129-story.html | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.theage.com.au/entertainment/books/colleen-mccullough-author-of-the-thorn-birds-dies-20150129-131dka.html|title=Colleen McCullough, author of The Thorn Birds, dies|author=Susan Wyndham|work=The Age|access-date=2015-01-30|archive-date=2015-02-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150201022336/http://www.theage.com.au/entertainment/books/colleen-mccullough-author-of-the-thorn-birds-dies-20150129-131dka.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="The New York Times 2015">{{cite web | title=Colleen McCullough, Author of ‘The Thorn Birds,’ Dies at 77 | website=The New York Times | date=2015-01-29 | url=https://www.nytimes.com/2015/01/30/books/colleen-mccullough-author-of-the-thorn-birds-dies-at-77.html | access-date=2021-09-03 | archive-date=2021-12-12 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211212154217/https://www.nytimes.com/2015/01/30/books/colleen-mccullough-author-of-the-thorn-birds-dies-at-77.html | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="McKinnell 2018">{{cite web | last=McKinnell | first=Jamie | title=ABC News | website=Colleen McCullough: Australian author's $2.1m estate left to her husband | date=2018-07-20 | url=https://www.abc.net.au/news/2018-07-20/colleen-mcullough-estatel-left-to-husband/10017042 | access-date=2021-09-03 | archive-date=2021-09-03 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210903054220/https://www.abc.net.au/news/2018-07-20/colleen-mcullough-estatel-left-to-husband/10017042 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

